// $Id$

(Note this test came originally from Prismtech's tao764_regression which
was tied into tao764, tao836, tao840 and tao870 tickets.)

Regression test for MIOP packet reassembly if a GIOP message is too big.

Expected successful output is below.

$> ./run_test.pl
MIOP object is <IOR:010000000100000000000000010000000300000040000000010100000d0000003232352e31302e31302e31300000bf4e01000000270000001c0000000101000007000000646f6d61696e0000010000000000000000000000>
Activated as <IOR:>
args to be used: -k 'file://server.ior' -p 100000 -t 1 -f 0 -c 10 -s 1000

Client finished successfully
args to be used: -k 'file://server.ior' -p 1000 -t 5 -f 0 -c 100 -s 100 -x

Client finished successfully

Server finished successfully.
